    "description": "An optional surface renders at a Stable (or LTS) public claim only when it carries a captured, within-freshness-SLO stable qualification packet, complete surface evidence, an owner sign-off, any waiver it relies on is unexpired, and the public claim it backs is itself at or above the cutline. An optional surface that lacks a stable qualification packet, whose packet breached its freshness SLO, whose surface evidence or capability is incomplete, whose waiver expired, or whose backing public claim is below the cutline renders a label below the cutline (beta, preview, withdrawn) and never inherits an adjacent qualified surface's label."
  },
